<p>The issue is with: Example #18 Sample View resource configuration</p>

<p>Adding the resources.view.basePath ini setting to the value of specified as:
APPLICATION_PATH "/views/scripts" ; at the time of writing</p>

<p>will set the base path to APPLICATION_PATH/views/scripts/scripts</p>

<p>The sample should be: 
resources.view.basePath = APPLICATION_PATH "/views"</p>

